AosUnitMessageV7

Type: object

Unit message model.

root header

AosUnitHeaderV7

Type: object

Aos Unit-Cloud message header

root header version

Protocol version

Type: const

The version of Unit-Cloud protocol.

Specific value: 7

root header systemId
Type: string

The unique system ID of the unit.
